songs.title: Pour Me
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Poor me, I'm floating out to sea
An opportunity that went by
Poor you, oh what you going to do
No what you going to do, you just cry
Oh, you always come undone
Try into the sun, you don't know why
Poor you, I know what you going to do
Come on love I'll see it through, I don't know why

[Chorus]
I hear you come nearer, I hear you but I don't understand
I hear you come nearer, I hear you but I don't understand

[Verse 2]
Poor me, now float me out to sea
Oh no just let it be, come on try
Poor you, oh what you going to do
Oh what you gonna do, you just cry

[Chorus]
I hear you come nearer, I hear you but I don't understand
I hear you come nearer, I hear you but I don't understand
I don't understand
I don't understand
Oooh, ahhhh, ahhhh
